{"tid":761004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放手一搏同放手離開 你會選擇...","createTime":"2018-07-30T04:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T16:28:00.000Z","uid":174405,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30e30be2e3966648570bbf92178cd20b4b841ed0","tid":761004,"uid":174405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"我選擇放手離開...<br />\n<br />\n對上一段感情6年4頂綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己成日諗係初戀，所以選擇放手一搏繼續一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果自己都懷疑自己到底係咪上世欠佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己一個人過咗一段時間<br />\n遇過好多好多人<br />\n但都冇諗住去展開新戀情<br />\n寧缺勿濫 寧缺勿濫 寧缺勿濫<br />\n<br />\n點知打機識咗你<br />\n以為遇到你會係人生中最幸福既事<br />\n點知你ex係呢段時間不停搵你，但你冇拒絕<br />\n一開始我同自己講，你同ex10年感情，唔係話斷就斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己初戀6年都好難一時三刻斷到哂所有野<br />\n用咗幾個月去搞清楚狀況同所有野<br />\n但我發覺如果真係要搞清楚，好多野其實要分清並唔難，只係做定唔做<br />\n<br />\n但我攰啦，我唔想感情用事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放手離開 轉身走人 希望你照顧好自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你ex係個好女仔 好好珍惜身邊的人呀<br />\n如果有機會，希望下次見到你係你拖住小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我有機會教你個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論我們最後生疏成什麼樣子，都要記得曾經對你的好，都是真的。 &mdash;&mdash; 後來的我們"},{"pid":"c12d79a9829d8dbb7f860d6e26ac9f9b229b674a","tid":761004,"uid":140798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"屌 祝咩福人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c68a2ca6f573b5ac641f8ad7af325b8c61c9b41","tid":761004,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"放唔低又點解要開始呢"},{"pid":"15909b5eb71f37c855fbe722c9aa34086d3c00bc","tid":761004,"uid":174405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c68a2ca6f573b5ac641f8ad7af325b8c61c9b41","tid":761004,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"放唔低又點解要開始呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"所以...我寧願自己走..."},{"pid":"23644d8192494c86459c898ab3bd768abde77d8b","tid":761004,"uid":174405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c12d79a9829d8dbb7f860d6e26ac9f9b229b674a","tid":761004,"uid":140798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"屌 祝咩福人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"唉...係到抒發一下...無朋友明白我"}]}